high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Move to the right and put the soap in the right sink.
Pick up the soap from the sink and bring it to the counter on the left.
Put the soap back on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet soap on the counter.

high_descs: Go forward and to the sink on your right.
Move right an go to the sink on the right.
Put the soap in the sink and get it wet.
Put the soap on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap on the counter.

high_descs: Move forward, then turn right and go to the counter between the two sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap, behind the hand soap.
Turn around, then turn left, then turn left again to face the sink.
Wash the soap inside of the sink.
Turn left move forward then turn right to face the sink.
Place the soap on the counter between the sinks, in front of the candle.
anns.task_desc: Put clean soap on the counter.
